{"tid":1317361,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"如果7.21有多過55萬人","createTime":"2019-07-14T18:22:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-19T22:09:16.000Z","uid":168003,"like":95,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"48f262b3f08b8eff7610f6b007818c7257ade7ee","tid":1317361,"uid":168003,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T18:22:21.000Z","msg":"政府呢排玩緊既輿論戰<br />\n就係想令中立同淺黃覺得勇武好暴力<br />\n7.21就係成績表 係俾林鄭睇下輿論戰既成果<br />\n<br />\n如果7.21有多過55萬人<br />\n係代表左香港人對勇武已經默認<br />\n對警權同政權完全失望<br />\n係淺黃同中立既全面回歸<br />\n係大眾主流既聲音<br />\n係10.1之前都逆轉唔到 咁中共就大濟<br />\n<br />\n如果7.21係少過55萬人<br />\n姐係話林鄭分化成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後所有措施會越黎越硬 因為已經變左小眾社運<br />\n之後就唔會再有機會對抗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家要諗點樣可以係個日之前拉番個勢出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e89fdd2b7d4e456cee3b34cdb3471dfe248e17e5","tid":1317361,"uid":60398,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T18:29:00.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">聽日又要佔領輿論，港台商台火力全開</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1316677\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1316677</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n0800-1000 香港電台第一台<br />\n千禧年代 / Phone in 電話: 1872311<br />\n<br />\n1700-1800 香港電台第一台<br />\n自由風自由Phone / Phone in 電話: 1872311<br />\n<br />\n0630-0700, 0715-1000 雷霆881 (陳志雲版)<br />\n0800-1000 叱咤903 (潘小濤版)<br />\n在晴朗的一天出發 / Phone in 電話: 1872881 (陳) / 1872903 (潘)<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我係入去商場食飯架<br />\n點解警察要用警棍打我呀？<br />\n<br />\n大家自己諗好大家嘅身份<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: pink;\">同場加映</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JiOnfAc.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJiOnfAc.png&h=39ea108e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"271d54415bf040d3b99a5adfaf2d5c65c985241a","tid":1317361,"uid":3852