果<br />\n<br />\n如果7.21有多過55萬人<br />\n係代表左香港人對勇武已經默認<br />\n對警權同政權完全失望<br />\n係淺黃同中立既全面回歸<br />\n係大眾主流既聲音<br />\n係10.1之前都逆轉唔到 咁中共就大濟<br />\n<br />\n如果7.21係少過55萬人<br />\n姐係話林鄭分化成功<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後所有措施會越黎越硬 因為已經變左小眾社運<br />\n之後就唔會再有機會對抗<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家要諗點樣可以係個日之前拉番個勢出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-14T20:32:29.000Z","msg":"7.21之前唔好再有暴力沖突事件，會嚇走啲老弱婦孺唔敢上街！"},{"pid":"e528ad9095fca2acc48ec07901384fb475ffcbe9","tid":1317361,"uid":258377,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-19T22:09:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">推哂d 有用嘅post 上嚟， 三毛死撚開DLLM<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/diu.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n721 15:00 維園見<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"}]}